This reproducibility report provides details about the artifact evaluation done with regards to the Artifact Description and Evaluation appendix of SC25 paper SIGMo: High-Throughput Batched Subgraph Isomorphism on GPUs for Molecular Matching by Gennaro Cordasco et al. The work was done as part of the Reproducibility Initiative of SC25. The author is a member of the SC25 Reproducibilty Committee.